            >
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center text-muted gap-2">
                <i class="ri-calendar-line me-1"></i>
                <span>18 Mar 2025</span>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center text-muted gap-2">
                <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-muted">
                  <i class="ri-user-line me-1"></i>
                  <span>By Azad Shaikh</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="card border p-0 mb-4"
            data-aos="fade-in"
            data-aos-delay="100"
            data-aos-duration="1000"
          >
            <img
              src="https://asterodigital.com/storage/local/aamf/cms/post/121/bootstrap-language.png"
              class="card-img-top"
              alt="Blog Image"
            />
            <div class="card-body p-3 p-md-4">
              <a
                href="https://asterodigital.com/coding/"
                class="text-decoration-none text-uppercase fs-6 fw-semibold">Coding</a
              >
              <h2 class="my-2">
                <a
                  href="https://asterodigital.com/coding/bootstrap-language-selector/"
                  class="text-decoration-none text-body fs-3"
                  >Bootstrap Language Selector: Implementation Guide</a
                >
              </h2>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                When launching a global product or website, providing language options is crucial
                for user accessibility. A well-designed language selector enhances user experience
